# WHOSRILA branded short links
# Format: /slug   destination-url   status-code
#
# Every current single now has a real page with a Feature.fm embed
# instead of a redirect (gratitude, forme, wineandbubble, outtaline,
# fullymeech, topformnodrums, kingston, bluenotes, protection, topform)
# — see each song's folder in this site. Made You is the same (/madeyou).
#
# Use this file going forward only for links you genuinely want to
# just forward elsewhere rather than host a page for — for example,
# a quick redirect straight to a Spotify profile or a one-off link
# for a feature/collab post.
#
# 302 = "temporary" — use this for anything that might change later.
# 301 = "permanent" — use this once a link is final for good.
#
# Drag this whole site folder onto the dropzone at the bottom of your
# site's Deploys page in Netlify. It picks up _redirects automatically.
